name: Experiment Or Die #24
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. Splitting this image across 2 layouts makes it even more unclear what the original images were... except of course the iconic battle for good and evil. Putting the 2 together adds some clarity to the color palette of the whole. Day 23 and 24 go together as I work on them both across the midnight cusp. IG: Nikejerk
